snippet.title: Gameplay Trailer "Toram Online"
snippet.description:
[Subscribe] https://bit.ly/bemmoch
[Gameplay Trailer]
Toram Online - MMORPG with Complete Freedom -

Toram Online, an MMORPG that allows you to go on adventures and connect with friends from around the world!
You may be able to beat the monster you couldn't beat alone by forming a party with your friends!
Let's explore the beautiful and vast 3D world with your friends!

- Create Your Own Characters!

Create and design your character with more than 500 billion customization options!
"This MMORPG doesn't have a "Job System".
You can build your character as you like with "Skill System".
As you progress through the game, you will even be able to customize your weapon abilities!

Dive into the vast world!

Official site https://en.toram.jp/

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/toram.jp

Google Play(Android) https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.asobimo.toramonline&hl=en

AppStore(iOS) https://apps.apple.com/us/app/toram-online/id988683886

steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1827180/_/
